    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ！　良かった、無事だったんだな\n落ちた時にどこか怪我したりはしなかったか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1666668892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。この通り、ピンピンしてます\n服はずぶ濡れになっちゃいましたけど……くしゅんっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……見てるこっちは本当に肝が冷えたんだぞ\nなんでいきなり、あんな無茶をしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……\n……あ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.4666665394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことより、犯人はどうなったんですか！？\nあちらも、警察の人が引き上げてくれたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "あの人、これからどうなるんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.8000030199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "田んぼは無事だったことですし、ご家族も心配しますし\n未遂ってことで、お説教で済めばいいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ、まだドッキリだって気付いてないのかな）\n（……あ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2566.6649184000007,
          "startTime": 49.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3666712123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-mobmen001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あのー……さっきは自分の不注意のせいで\n危険な目に遭わせてしまいまして、すみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5000005086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あなたも無事で良かったです\nもう、人を脅してお金を得ようとしたらダメですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと反省してもらって……あれ？\nなんで、胸元にピンマイクを付けてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.2333353679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、テレビの演者じゃないと必要ないのに\n……ん？　んんん？　もしかして、今日の事件って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5000045458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すまん！　水路に飛び込んだことで頭が一杯になって\nすみれに、ドッキリのことを説明するのを忘れてた！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6666748047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ドッキリ！？\n確かに今日の事件、おかしなところはあったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "周りの人達がなかなか避難しなかったし、素人の私に\n爆弾を持った犯人との交渉を任せようとするし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9333485603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "田んぼのど真ん中でダイナマイトを巻いてたところから\nツッコんでいいんだぞ、すみれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-mobmen002.m4a",
      "text": "わははは、ですよねぇ\nみんなで事件のネタ考えているうちに\n盛り上がっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……私は、山形のみんなと\n田んぼの安全を揺るがす大事件だと思ってたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.6666631062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "ううう～……{user}さんの馬鹿！！\nみんなして私を騙して、酷いっちゃ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.266662089,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.00457770002,
          "startTime": 138.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0166747729
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0166747729
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.2666747729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そして俺達は、山形での仕事を終えて東京に戻り）\n（二週間後、舞台『空の宝石』の公演日がやって来た）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "開演まであと少しか……でも、すみれはさすがだな\n本番前なのに、凄く楽しそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.2666707356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないですよ。本番前はいつも\n失敗したらどうしようって、心臓がバクバクしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、今回も緊張はしてますけど、それ以上に\n早くみんなに見てもらいたいって、わくわくしちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.9000192958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "この舞台の稽古が始まってから、演技に悩んでたけど\nすっかり自信が付いたみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
